00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:55.677
does not exist at f of
x or as we approach 8.

00:06:55.677 --> 00:06:56.760
So let me write that down.

00:06:56.760 --> 00:07:01.330
The limit of f of x,
as x approaches 8--

00:07:01.330 --> 00:07:04.370
because these two things
are not the same value--

00:07:04.370 --> 00:07:05.875
this does not exist.

